description:
As the poll dates are set to be announced - we got news that Election Commissioner Arun Goel has abruptly resigned without giving any reasons....now from the 3 member Election Commission - only one remains .... as the nation is going for elections. 

The opposition already has been finding things difficult - but even on its own - there are many issues that remain unresolved .... how READY is the opposition for the Lok Sabha 2024 Polls??
